works.description: Glock, one of the leading global manufacturers of pistols and accessories, is celebrating its 25th anniversary in the U.S. with a limited edition Silver Anniversary Glock 17 Gen4 (9×19) pistol. The company started its operations in the United States in 1986. The Glock 17 in caliber 9×19 is one of the most widely used law enforcement pistols worldwide. The 25th Anniversary Glock 17 Gen4 features a custom 25th Anniversary logo in silver on the grip, and an inscription on the slide.
